title: Woman detained after climbing fence at Lincolnshire RAF base
title_page: Woman detained after climbing fence at Lincolnshire RAF base - BBC News
maintext:
A woman has been detained after climbing over the fence of an RAF base where a multi-nation military training exercise was taking place.
The woman was stopped by military police as she headed towards the runway at RAF Waddington, the Ministry of Defence said.
They added that the incident "lasted less than ten minutes and did not impact on operations".
